        "heading": "The wood is chosen before the first line is ever drawn.",
        "body_1": "Before sketching anything, I go see the material. I pick my boards one by one from two sawmills in the Montérégie, based on the grain, the knots and the natural tone. A dining table isn't designed the same way whether the ash leans toward honey or toward grey.",
